{"tid":1630804,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"admin del post 唔該","createTime":"2019-10-06T13:43:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T13:58:25.000Z","uid":110611,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f923ff602f5b8597dded4768aee8d3b0ff7af033","tid":1630804,"uid":110611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:43:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c302fc8203044c7491d5e4a51848a1ce41fe3c7e","tid":1630804,"uid":110611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:44:27.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"7bd2cf4b95afea32c6e605827f71693395b4c435","tid":1630804,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:45:16.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"8a64bffc6ab9cc2ff09468cd19ee7bc5fb5d3776","tid":1630804,"uid":110611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:45:34.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"82c9a8eeba689ee293befe070ff42d50e87a97ed","tid":1630804,"uid":110611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:46:56.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"8e4025c96ec974ad4af154b432beb81ae3d23850","tid":1630804,"uid":110611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:47:55.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"65212c35bfebd492a51445320b1ddfdb081a8ba8","tid":1630804,"uid":110611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:48:32.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"30c58f9157597207015dd9c771f1739f9ddbbf81","tid":1630804,"uid":110611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:56:06.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"57f92ea7f2b5301f434eae5df7d4ee128409b47e","tid":1630804,"uid":110611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:58:25.000Z","msg":"7/10"}]}